org.linqs.psl.model.formula.traversal

Class FormulaGrounder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.model.formula.traversal.AbstractFormulaTraverser
      • org.linqs.psl.model.formula.traversal.FormulaGrounder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FormulaTraverser

    public class FormulaGrounder
extends AbstractFormulaTraverser
    FormulaGrounder is an object capable of traversing a Formula, replacing Variables with values specified in the VariableAssignment or ResultList passed to the constructor.
